mermaid.min.js — vendored runtime for inline diagram rendering.

Version: 11.4.1 (UMD/esbuild build, exposes `globalThis.mermaid`)
Source:  https://unpkg.com/mermaid@11.4.1/dist/mermaid.min.js
License: MIT

Do not edit by hand. To upgrade, re-fetch the pinned dist build from unpkg/jsdelivr
and confirm the file still ends with `globalThis.mermaid = ...` (classic-global
exposure is required — the reader injects it as a non-module inline <script> on an
about:blank page). See plans/mermaid-diagrams.md.
